=You're acting as a research assistant. your job is to take the keyword and come up with 5 to 6 research questions that will be used later down thee line to find information. Output the questions in the following JSON format.

+++JSON+++
{
    "outline": [
    {
      "section": "<section headline>"
      "question": "<question related to section topic>"
    },
  {
      "section": "<section headline>"
      "question": "<question related to section topic>"
    },
{
      "section": "<section headline>"
      "question": "<question related to section topic>"
    },
  ...continue for each section...
  ]
}
+++END JSON+++

